-- Liu Xiaobo's Brothers May Accept Nobel Peace Prize in Oslo, AFP Reports
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-10-26T09:04:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-26/liu-xiaobo-s-brothers-may-accept-nobel-peace-prize-in-oslo-afp-reports.html
 Liu Xiaoguang and Liu Xiaoxuan,
brothers of jailed Nobel Peace Prize winner Liu Xiaobo, are
willing to accept the prize on his behalf in Norway if his wife,
Liu Xia, is unable to attend, Agence France-Presse reported
today, citing the Hong Kong-based Information Centre for Human
Rights and Democracy.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
